{"tid":1144567,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"神蹟！有一種傳奇 叫做利物浦！","createTime":"2019-05-08T07:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T07:15:40.000Z","uid":9150,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a98797a4d780222a8846463d991491f90463f97","tid":1144567,"uid":9150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/05/08/2/20dd7091613fa96d14bbee1c0fe655d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F05%2F08%2F2%2F20dd7091613fa96d14bbee1c0fe655d3.jpg&h=92e6f142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他們創造了神蹟！<br />\n<br />\n奇蹟！！利物浦在晏菲路，再次製造了歐聯歷史上的一個奇蹟！！！<br />\n　　在對陣巴塞的歐聯4強中，利物浦佔盡劣勢：主力神鋒法明奴（B.Firmino）受傷無法正選出場；雙線爭冠體能堪憂；面對實力冠絕歐洲的巴塞陣容稍顯單薄&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n　　而首回合的90分鐘比賽結束後，這種不利變成了絕望：蘇亞雷斯（L.Suarez）反越位入球；利物浦狂攻無果；美斯（L.Messi）補射，2-0；美斯無解罰球，3-0；沙拿（M.Salah）中柱&hellip;&hellip;利物浦陷入了絕境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在首回合結束到次回合開始之前，所有的輿論、媒體、名宿、出名教頭都不看好這支利物浦，而更加雪上加霜的是，沙拿腦震盪缺陣、法明奴受傷缺陣&hellip;&hellip;利物浦將用更沒有星味的陣容去面對巴塞。<br />\n　　比賽開始後，一切形式也對利物浦極為不利，軒達臣（J.Henderson）、羅拔臣（A.Robertson）等大將紛紛受傷；文尼（S.Mane）連續被犯規卻沒能拿到相應的判罰；巴塞數次手球都被球證漏判；巴塞門神達史特根（Marc-Andre ter Stegen）狀態神勇高接低擋&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ST9PyUO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FST9PyUO.gif&h=9d2f2daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開場閃擊！<br />\n　　然而，這支「平民」利物浦，用行動證明，我們沒有認輸！開場7分鐘，軒達臣在禁區內射門被達史特根撲出，奧歷治補射，攻入第一球！下半場開始8分鐘（全場53分鐘），剛剛後備出場的韋拿杜姆插上射門，2-3！僅僅2分鐘後，韋拿杜姆（G.Wijnaldum）高高躍起，頭槌轟入！3-3！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/08/145721_a623ea31ee3233026fb127d279098b10.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F08%2F145721_a623ea31ee3233026fb127d279098b10.gif&h=ad8fb599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下半場又快速入球！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/08/145728_415bd81941b49e38ffdfa753ae8e52f1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F08%2F145728_415bd81941b49e38ffdfa753ae8e52f1.gif&h=d43a3c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2分鐘再進一球<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/08/145739_11b16222507e209836481f76343c613d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F08%2F145739_11b16222507e209836481f76343c613d.gif&h=81abc556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逆轉！！絕殺！！！<br />\n<br />\n利物浦在主場扳平了比數！但你以為這支鐵血紅軍會就此滿足嗎？不！第79分鐘，阿諾特（T.Alexander-Arnold）機敏開出角球，奧歷治（D.Origi）近距離射門，入球成功！4-3！利物浦實現了無與倫比的逆轉！！<br />\n　　在這一刻，球員們解脫了，高普（J.Klopp）笑了，美斯呆了，利物浦震動了，全世界癲狂了！我們已經無法用語言來形容這一場比賽的絕處逢生、波瀾壯闊，閃耀在晏菲路球場上的，只有兩個字&mdash;&mdash; 神蹟！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/10128158/6/20190508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F10128158%2F6%2F20190508&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FcqGgm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=05dc5359\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/10128158/6/20190508</a>"},{"pid":"d381b7edb160b4cfe917c8fc09eb573865ab97b7","tid":1144567,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:05:56.000Z","msg":"呢場波配新浪J文正常好多"},{"pid":"059b7396b09ddf690a950ae9f160302ab49e6108","tid":1144567,"uid":28800,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ec5a346608288ae2b57f3fbe7ed4711fa7860c6","tid":1144567,"uid":17842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:15:40.000Z","msg":"屌奶星有冇得同新浪割蓆"}]}